================================================================================
i3dToObjx (bundled as bin/i3dToObjx.exe)
================================================================================

The bundled .exe is built from a modified version of the I3DShapesTool-OBJx
project, which is itself a fork of the original I3DShapesTool.

Original project:
    I3DShapesTool
    Author:  Daniel Hultgren (Donkie)
    Source:  https://github.com/Donkie/I3DShapesTool

Upstream fork:
    I3DShapesTool-OBJx
    Author:  VidhosticeSDK
    Source:  https://github.com/VidhosticeSDK/I3DShapesTool-OBJx

Local modifications by Nadine Brinkmann:
    Source:  https://github.com/nadine-brinkmann/i3d-to-objx
    Changes: see commit history; among others, added spline export (patches/03).

